Blade Runner 2049 is an upcoming American neo-noir science fiction film directed by Denis Villeneuve and written by Hampton Fancher and Michael Green .
It is the sequel to 1982 's Blade Runner and stars Ryan Gosling and Harrison Ford , who is reprising his role as Rick Deckard , with Ana de Armas , Mackenzie Davis , Sylvia Hoeks , Lennie James , Carla Juri , Robin Wright , Dave Bautista and Jared Leto in supporting roles .
The film is set to be released in the United States on October 6 , 2017 , in 2D , 3D and IMAX 3D .
Warner Bros. .
Pictures will distribute the film in the United States , while Columbia Pictures will handle international distribution .